<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: abandoned settlement -->
  <AbandonedSettlement.label>廢棄的據點</AbandonedSettlement.label>
  <!-- EN: The gravcore energy signature is coming from somewhere in this settlement. Explore the abandoned buildings to find the gravcore. -->
  <AbandonedSettlement.description>重力核心的能量信號來自這個據點的某個地方。探索廢棄的建築以找到重力核心。</AbandonedSettlement.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <AbandonedSettlement.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：重力核心</AbandonedSettlement.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: ancient reactor -->
  <AncientReactor.label>遠古反應堆</AncientReactor.label>
  <!-- EN: An ancient reactor is hidden within nearby ruins. The reactor is cracked and leaking toxic fallout over the whole region. Locate and disable the reactor to obtain a gravcore and stop the fallout. -->
  <AncientReactor.description>一個遠古反應堆藏在附近的廢墟中。反應堆已破裂並洩漏出毒霧霾至整個地區。尋找並終止該反應堆以獲取重力核心並停止霧霾。</AncientReactor.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <AncientReactor.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：重力核心</AncientReactor.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: ancient stockpile -->
  <AncientStockpile.label>遠古儲藏庫</AncientStockpile.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the energy signature of a gravcore emanating from an ancient underground stockpile. The location is marked on the world map.\n\nObtain gravcores and gravlite panels to increase the size of your gravship. -->
  <AncientStockpile.description>你已經偵測到來自遠古地下儲藏庫的重力核心能量信號。位置已標記在世界地圖上。\n\n獲取重力核心和重力板來擴張你的重力船。</AncientStockpile.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <AncientStockpile.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：重力核心</AncientStockpile.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: crashed mechanoid platform -->
  <CrashedMechanoidPlatform.label>墜毀的機械族平台</CrashedMechanoidPlatform.label>
  <!-- EN: The remains of an orbital platform are strewn nearby. Be careful, the wreckage contains hostile mechanoids.\n\nThe gravcore signal is coming from somewhere within the crash site. -->
  <CrashedMechanoidPlatform.description>一個軌道平台的殘骸散落在附近。小心，殘骸裡有敵對的機械族。 \n\n墜毀地點的某處有重力核心發出的訊號。</CrashedMechanoidPlatform.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <CrashedMechanoidPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：重力核心</CrashedMechanoidPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: frozen terraformer -->
  <FrozenTerraformer.label>冷凍地形改造器</FrozenTerraformer.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the energy signature of a gravcore. The gravcore is powering a malfunctioning ancient terraformer. Its location is marked on the world map.\n\nThe terraformer is cooling the local region to dangerously low temperatures. Be prepared for cold weather.\n\nObtain gravcores and gravlite panels to increase the size of your gravship. -->
  <FrozenTerraformer.description>你已經偵測到重力核心的能量信號。重力核心正在為一個故障的遠古地形改造器供電。其位置已標記在世界地圖上。\n\n地形改造器正在將當地氣溫降至危險的低溫。準備好應對寒冷天氣。\n\n獲取重力核心和重力板來增加你的重力船大小。</FrozenTerraformer.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <FrozenTerraformer.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：重力核心</FrozenTerraformer.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: cave system -->
  <InsectLair.label>洞穴系統</InsectLair.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the energy signature of a gravcore emanating from a cave system deep underground. The entrance to the cave system is marked on the world map.\n\nObtain gravcores and gravlite paneling to upgrade your gravship. -->
  <InsectLair.description>你已經偵測到來自深地下洞穴系統的重力核心能量信號。洞穴系統的入口已標記在世界地圖上。\n\n獲取重力核心和重力板來升級你的重力船。</InsectLair.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <InsectLair.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：重力核心</InsectLair.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: mechanoid relay -->
  <MechanoidRelay.label>機械族中繼器</MechanoidRelay.label>
  <!-- EN: The gravcore energy signature is coming from a mechanoid communication relay here. Disassemble it to acquire the gravcore. -->
  <MechanoidRelay.description>重力核心的能量信號來自於這裡的一個機械族通信中繼器。拆解它以獲取重力核心。</MechanoidRelay.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <MechanoidRelay.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：重力核心</MechanoidRelay.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: abandoned orbital platform -->
  <OrbitalAncientPlatform.label>廢棄的軌道平台</OrbitalAncientPlatform.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the energy signature of a gravcore.\n\nBe careful - orbital locations are extremely dangerous. Ensure your gravship is fully enclosed with airtight walls and equip your colonists with vacsuits. Plan your return trip, as living in orbit for long periods is very difficult. -->
  <OrbitalAncientPlatform.description>你已經偵測到重力核心的能量信號。\n\n小心——軌道位置極為危險。確保你的重力船配備氣密墻，並為你的殖民者配備真空服。計畫你的回程，因為長時間在軌道上生活非常困難。</OrbitalAncientPlatform.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <OrbitalAncientPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：重力核心</OrbitalAncientPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: mechanoid platform -->
  <OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.label>機械族平台</OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the energy signature of a gravcore on this platform. There is a heavy mechanoid presence.\n\nBe careful, orbital locations are extremely dangerous. Ensure your gravship is fully enclosed with airtight walls and equip your colonists with vacsuits. Plan your return trip, as living in orbit for long periods is very difficult. -->
  <OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.description>你已經偵測到該平台上的重力核心能量信號。有大量的機械族存在。\n\n小心，軌道位置極為危險。確保你的重力船配備氣密墻，並為你的殖民者配備真空服。計畫你的回程，因為長時間在軌道上生活非常困難。</OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.description>
  <!-- EN: Contains: Gravcore -->
  <OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>包含：重力核心</OrbitalMechanoidPlatform.mainPartAllThreatsLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: mechhive -->
  <OrbitalMechhive.label>機械巢穴</OrbitalMechhive.label>
  <!-- EN: You have detected the mechhive in orbit above the planet. Its location is marked on the world map.\n\nThe mechhive is the center of mechanoid intelligence and directs mechanoids across planet. If shut down, it will disable mechanoids planet-wide. Alternatively, you may be able to use the mechhive for your own purposes.\n\nBe warned, mechhives are extremely dangerous. Finish exploring other locations first and ensure you're prepared for a long stay in orbit. -->
  <OrbitalMechhive.description>你已經偵測到位於行星上方軌道的機械巢穴。其位置已標記在世界地圖上。\n\n機械巢穴是機械族智能的中心，指揮整個行星的機械族。若將其關閉，它將使整個行星的機械族失效。或者，你可能能夠將機械巢穴用於自己的目的。\n\n注意，機械巢穴極其危險。先完成其他地點的探索，確保你準備好在軌道上長時間停留。</OrbitalMechhive.description>
  
</LanguageData>